data.description: Great location with grand spaces. Private cul-de-sac with majestic views. An actual living room and a front bedroom that adapts to an office, library, music room...you name it! Newer stainless appliances and solid surface counter tops with raised bar. Laundry stubbed on main in 3rd bedroom for a multitude of uses; Sink still there; I know you can image. Over-sized great room with large, open kitchen. French doors lead you to your covered deck with stairs to yard & garage. Quite and serene backyard looks into cul-de-sac. New high efficiency furnace and 2 water heaters. Insulated garage has gas heater with H/C spigots; extra height / width along with attic storage. Seller is ready to entertain offers!
